reel\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2886}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You need to be constantly updating that and sending it to people.\\\"\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Teenagers 'planned to attack man who thought he was meeting girl, 16' Teenagers and taxi driver killed in head-on crash named locally Teenagers thought to be among victims of Greater Manchester head-on crash 20 years on, this cult fragrance brand is still ahead of the curve Feedback from guests highlighted the event's success in demystifying the often overwhelming process of career planning.\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 3354, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"man\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 2988}, {\"ngram\": \"girl\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3020}, {\"ngram\": \"16' Teenagers and taxi driver\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3051}, {\"ngram\": \"head-on crash\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3075}, {\"ngram\": \"locally Teenagers\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3099}, {\"ngram\": \"victims\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3127}, {\"ngram\": \"Greater Manchester head-on crash\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3163}, {\"ngram\": \"this cult fragrance brand\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3202}, {\"ngram\": \"the curve Feedback\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3239}, {\"ngram\": \"guests\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3251}, {\"ngram\": \"the event's success\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3283}, {\"ngram\": \"the often overwhelming process\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3330}, {\"ngram\": \"career planning\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One 16-year-old visitor from south London said: \\\"I came here feeling pretty lost about what to do after GCSEs, but now I have got loads of ideas.\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3390, \"end\": 3396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9998994035215313, \"rank\": 0.00010022852207923499, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\",